latestPosts.caption:
Must Try Viral Drink in Thailand🇹🇭

Share with someone who is travelling to Thailand🥂

You have to try this Viral 7-11 Drink when in Thailand!

And it shall cost you just 35 Thai Baht (₹88 or 1$)

How to make it :-

- Go to any #711store in Thailand
- Take Banana Milk for 12 Baht
- Take Sunshine Chocolate Milk for 13 Baht
- Take one glass with ice for 10 Baht
- Mix it up
- Enjoy and share this with a friend
